Disabilitar SElinux0
ver artigo em http://docs.fedoraproject.org/en-US/Fedora/13/html/Security-Enhanced_Linux/sect-Security-Enhanced_Linux-Working_with_SELinux-Enabling_and_Disabling_SELinux.html
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Lista todos os usuários
# cat /etc/passwd | awk -F ":" '{print $1}'
